
	VOMS ENVIRONMENT FOR WLCG

Description: 
voms-config-wlcg is a package to setup a VOMS environment for wlcg.


Support:
This package is provided for an easy deployment of a wlcg environment.
It installs vomses and vomsdir files for the usual WLCG Virtual Organizations :

- alice
- atlas
- cms
- dteam
- lhcb
- geant4
- sixtrack

Official list here : http://wlcg.web.cern.ch/getting-started/VO

Other VO (ex: from EGI or OSGC ) are not supported officialy, but can be still be included if needed.
Please contact us for more details.

Usage:
- Install EGI trust anchor repository or WLCG one 
	- https://wiki.egi.eu/wiki/EGI_IGTF_Release
	- http://linuxsoft.cern.ch/LCG-CAs/current/
- Install voms-client voms-config-wlcg lcg-CA
- Rock & roll  


Contact:
lcgutil-devel@cern.ch

